#  PHASE 1: Laravel Setup + Common Login System

---

## Step 1: Install Laravel

```bash
composer create-project laravel/laravel ecommerce-app
cd ecommerce-app
php artisan serve
```

---

## Step 2: Setup Database

In `.env`:

```env
DB_DATABASE=ecommerce
DB_USERNAME=root
DB_PASSWORD=
```

Then:

```bash
php artisan migrate
```

---

## Step 3: Create Users Table (Modify)

```bash
php artisan make:migration add_role_status_to_users_table
```

Edit migration:

```php
public function up()
{
    Schema::table('users', function (Blueprint $table) {
        $table->enum('role', ['admin', 'user'])->default('user');
        $table->boolean('is_approved')->default(false);
    });
}
```

Run:

```bash
php artisan migrate
```

